Class NetworkSetupScreen

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.stage.Window
      • javafx.stage.Stage
        • NetworkSetupScreen
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.event.EventTarget

    class NetworkSetupScreen
extends javafx.stage.Stage
    The Network Setup/Config window that allows the player to choose how to set up their game. Displays all network options and saves the user's choices to be received by the game when the window is closed.
    Author:
    Yosef Jacobson
